|mplayer file=$in| 

--- model transcode_filter
|mplayer file=$in| --> y

   y --> |rgb2gray| --> |derivative| --> y_dot --> |posneg| --> yd
   
   y_dot --> |abs| --> |scale| --> ydabs
   
   
   y,yd,ydabs --> |grid cols=2| --> |mencoder file=$out|
